description:
Be captivated by this 2-year-old family home from the moment you enter, fusing a low-maintenance lifestyle with contemporary styling and finishes such as the well-equipped kitchen overlooking the blank canvas backyard.

The home's intelligent design provides a king-sized master bedroom with an en-suite and walk-in robe, while also positioning the kid's rooms at the opposite end, creating a parent's retreat to truly relax.

The stunning sun-drenched open-plan living area is both expansive and indulgent with a well-thought-out layout that will allow an effortless flow for indoor/outdoor entertaining.

* 40 minutes to Newcastle CBD
* As short as a 10-minute drive to some of the best vineyards in the Hunter valley has to offer.
* Near new home at only two years old
* Keep the kids entertained with only a short walk to Carmichael Park
